    user-agents

    Shuffle A Random UserAgent

    curl -s https://www.nr1.nu/archive/useragents/user_agents.txt|shuf -n1

    Add below code in your script

    useragent="$(curl -s https://www.nr1.nu/archive/useragents/user_agents.txt\ 
            |shuf -n1)"
shuf -e "${useragent}"
